{"tid":368350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援良心犯大遊行籌得250萬港元 將設基金支援16名良心犯及其親友","createTime":"2017-08-21T13:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T16:16:53.000Z","uid":22349,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd39cca616287cf6c1218161b2792e4ed8f1da3","tid":368350,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"大批港人昨逼爆灣仔，聲援重奪公民廣場案、反東北案等被政府窮追猛打下淪為階下囚的人士，用行動告訴良心犯，港人為你們而驕傲，你們從不孤單。主辦單位指參與遊行人數遠超預期，是自傘運後最多港人出席的遊行集會。不少遊行人士踴躍捐款，社民連主席吳文遠表示，今次籌款無分政黨，是統一以大會名義籌款，款項用作支援被捕者。「十六在囚抗爭者支援小組」表示，昨日籌得2,515,690元，並將用於支援囚友、其親友及案件上訴費用。<br />\n<br />\n支援小組感謝大家參與昨天遊行及捐款支援16人，包括東北13人及雙學三子公廣案，他們正籌備成立基金，稍後會詳細說明及公佈網上持續募款的收款戶口。"},{"pid":"917346555de931506d6b7067b1188a3292c03e68","tid":368350,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170821&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57109205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170821%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57109205&d=ZXOFqNCCuWIl91%2F%2FYo6SXm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2e64e982\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170821%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57109205&h=e348edd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170821&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57109205</a>"},{"pid":"261fb701233c043dfd80c76e144adadc4734978d","tid":368350,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"人地為錢咋 傻仔仲要幫人抬橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e96a8429f1ba432138d96200b1646d0a3957d8c","tid":368350,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170821/large/1503313373_4fad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-pap